Package: DynDocModel
Version: 0.0-1
Title: A Model for Dynamic Documents
Description: A document model for non-linear dynamic documents implemented in R. This alloows one to read in documents from a number of sources (knitr, IPython Notebooks, XDynDocs, etc) and operate on them, adding additional structure in the form of Tasks, branching structure (Alternative Implementations/Approaches for Tasks/subTasks), declared interactivity, etc.
Author: Gabriel Becker, Duncan Temple Lang
Depends: methods, RAutoGenRunTime, RJSONIO
Suggests: XDynDocs
Maintainer: Gabriel Becker <gmbecker@ucdavis.edu>
License: GPL
